title: 11 Jamie Eason: The World's Fittest Model on Healthy Living and Persistence
description: The World's Fittest Model visits The School of Greatness podcast to discuss fitness, faith and perseverance. Despite being pregnant during the interview, our guest is still a sought after model for magazine covers. Not only is she continuing to find success as a model, she is maintaining that passion for all the opportunities that the future holds in […]
author: podcast@schoolofgreatness.com (Lewis Howes)
